ps/2066490/extras/249ff88c5527c37e2f760e2f1852075c.webm?t=1701889368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066490/extras/249ff88c5527c37e2f760e2f1852075c.mp4?t=1701889368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Absolutely ZERO microtransactions or DLC.  All future content will be free. </li></ul>",
